name: Middle Eastern Delight
description:
A delicious blend of wood, musk, coconut, citrus, black currant and fig, this scent takes you on a journey through the prolific Middle East by producing a dark, fragrant resin while embodying the potency of traditional incense. Fig, Black Currant, Citrus, Coconut, Bergamot and Musk.

s'Adonner Candles are made from 100% natural soy wax; zinc/lead free cotton wick

Dimensions: 2 3/4"D x 4"H
Weight: 8.5oz.
Burn Time: 50 hours
